OL,3,CMan charged after six hurt in hospital
OL,5,FA man has been charged after six
OL,6,Fpeople were allegedly assaulted with a
OL,7,Fweapon inside of a hospital.
OL,9,FOmar Momand, originally from
OL,10,FAfghanistan but now of Newton-le-
OL,11,FWillows, has been charged with a
OL,12,Fnumber of offences including four
OL,13,Fcounts of section 18 wounding and
OL,14,Fpossession of an offensive weapon.
OL,16,FPolice were called to Newton Community
OL,17,FHospital on 30 December 2025 after
OL,18,Freceiving reports that a man had
OL,19,Fassualted six people with a weapon and
OL,20,Fcaused damage to the building.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
