OL,3,CMan charged after six hurt in hospital
OL,5,FMomand, of Collingwood Court on
OL,6,FBradlegh Road, has also been accused
OL,7,Fof attempted section 18 wounding,
OL,8,Factual bodily harm, affray, criminal
OL,9,Fdamage, possession of an offensive
OL,10,Fweapon and a controlled class B drug.
OL,12,FHe is due to appear at South Sefton
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday 18
OL,14,FMarch 2026.
